{"tid":2451883,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[日劇] 有冇人鍾意坂元裕二嘅作品？","createTime":"2021-03-18T11:59:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-22T16:47:40.000Z","uid":90596,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"daf44271ace4ee6b0967f7d9d6afcff041b4995e","tid":2451883,"uid":90596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T11:59:44.000Z","msg":"佢嘅作品風格鮮明，好有佢獨有嗰陣徐<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stretching.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好鍾意佢描繪人與人之間微妙嘅關係同互動，描繪得好細膩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n寫嘅主題有點深度，寫人性寫得幾立體，再配以意味深長、精闢獨到嘅對白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n亦都鍾意佢劇入面會用好多寓言同隱喻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇同好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b2616ed3b4402e472d95b98d920a0a550cb0e75","tid":2451883,"uid":123264,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T12:00:52.000Z","msg":"有無具體作品推荐下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ef426517020ba887947ecfa12be73f43a7acfb4","tid":2451883,"uid":90596,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"7b2616ed3b4402e472d95b98d920a0a550cb0e75","tid":2451883,"uid":123264,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T12:00:52.000Z","msg":"有無具體作品推荐下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T12:22:41.000Z","msg":"我自己暫時嚟講最鍾意 四重奏<br />\n(可能因為係入坑作)<br />\n係我少數會翻睇第2次嘅劇<br />\n當年好似都hit過下，好多人討論啲對白<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係講四個主角因為一次「偶遇」，<br />\n而咁啱佢哋玩開嘅樂器正好form到一隊quartet，咁就成咗事 並四個一齊生活嘞<br />\n佢哋嘅目標就係可以用音樂嚟揾食<br />\n<br />\n但其實佢哋四個又各有「陰謀」，<br />\n之後又發展到全員都單戀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就係有個咁樣少少荒誕嘅設定<br />\n以算係喜劇嘅形式，又帶有少少懸疑嘅元素，<br />\n去入面探討夢想與現實、友情、愛情/婚姻、人與人之間嘅相處 等哲理<br />\n睇到最尾兩集我又喊又笑，真係百感交集<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\